# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html) (though for an Apps Script project, versioning might be more date-based or feature-based initially).

## [1.0.0] - 2025-05-22 

### Added

*   **Initial Release of Google Sheets Quiz Management & Canvas Uploader!**
*   **Question Selection Module (`QuestionShuffler`):**
    *   Configuration via `SelectQuestions_Config` sheet to specify source sheets, number of questions, lecture ranges, and questions per lecture.
    *   Ability to mark selected questions with "Do Not Pick Again" in source sheets based on `ID`.
    *   Outputs selected questions to a `Selected Questions` sheet.
    *   Supports flexible header row and data start row in `SelectQuestions_Config`.
*   **Canvas Quiz Creator Module (`CanvasQuizCreator`):**
    *   Configuration via `CanvasQuiz_Config` sheet for Canvas API details, course ID, quiz title.
    *   Supports assigning different point values per question type (TF, MC, ES, Default) based on `ID` prefixes.
    *   Creates quizzes in Canvas using questions from the `Selected Questions` sheet (or other specified sheet).
    *   Handles True/False (`true_false_question`), Multiple Choice (`multiple_choice_question`), Multiple Answers (`multiple_answers_question`), and Essay (`essay_question`) question types for Canvas.
    *   Correctly sets answers for True/False questions based on sheet data.
    *   Calculates and updates total quiz points in Canvas based on successfully added questions.
    *   Creates quizzes as **UNPUBLISHED**.
*   **User Interface:**
    *   Custom "Extra Menu" in Google Sheets for easy access to "Select Questions" and "Create Quiz on Canvas" functionalities.
    *   (If implemented) Progress toasts and summary dialogs for user feedback.
    *   Detailed "Instructions" sheet template provided for setup and usage.
*   **Configuration:**
    *   Dedicated configuration sheets: `SelectQuestions_Config`, `CanvasQuiz_Config`.
    *   Constants defined for sheet names and column headers for maintainability.
*   **Error Handling:**
    *   Checks for missing configuration sheets and required columns.
    *   Validation of key configuration parameters.
    *   Logging of warnings and errors.
*   **Documentation:**
    *   Initial `README.md` for project overview, setup, and usage.
    *   `LICENSE.md` (MIT License suggested).
    *   `.gitignore` for local development with tools like `clasp`.
    *   This `CHANGELOG.md`.
*   **Code Structure:**
    *   Modular design with `QuestionShuffler` and `CanvasQuizCreator` objects.
    *   (If implemented) `UiUtils.gs` for UI helper functions.

